Oxidative Stress in Parkinson's Disease: Potential Benefits of Antioxidant 
Supplementation.

Percário S(1), da Silva Barbosa A(1), Varela ELP(1), Gomes ARQ(1), Ferreira 
MES(1), de Nazaré Araújo Moreira T(1), Dolabela MF(2).

Author information:
(1)Oxidative Stress Research Laboratory, Institute of Biological Sciences, 
